title: Wet Seal Is Closing All 171 of Its Stores (Bye, Middle School Self)
text: — Kasia❤️Emerald (@KasiaEmerald) January 27, 2017 1st #AmericanApparel , now #WetSeal . RIP to my tween days, window shopping for hours w/ just $11 & a dream. https://t.co/M013g4q8yC — Christine M. Carter (@cmichelcarter) January 27, 2017 Aw, #wetseal is closing. They sold so many things Mormon moms wouldn't let their daughters wear but we shopped there anyway ; ) — Katie Clifford (@replikate) January 27, 2017 Wow, #wetseal is trending. The memories.... pic.twitter.com/Aid2APoQBo — Starland Ballroom (@starlandNJ) January 27, 2017 First Casual Corner. Then the Limited. Now Wet Seal. i don't know if i want to live in a world without Casual Corner, The Limited, Wet Seal
